@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Helvetica
skinparam RoundCorner 14

hexagon "**AGENT**\nAI-as-a-product" as agent #00D2DD

rectangle "**1. Expose**\ndecisions & actions" as a1 #DAF6F9
rectangle "**2. Consume**\ncontext" as a2 #DAF6F9
rectangle "**3. Reason**\n& decide\n(code, not directives)" as a3 #DAF6F9
rectangle "**4. Be discoverable**\nmanifest, registry" as a4 #DAF6F9
rectangle "**5. Manage**\nits lifecycle" as a5 #DAF6F9
rectangle "**6. Trace**\ndecisions" as a6 #DAF6F9
rectangle "**7. Be governable**\naccess, kill switch" as a7 #DAF6F9

a1 -- agent
a2 -- agent
a3 -- agent
a4 -- agent
a5 -- agent
a6 -- agent
a7 -- agent

note bottom of agent
  An agent that does not offer these 7 affordances
  is a **prototype**, not a product.
  It cannot join the mesh.
end note

@enduml
